data.meta_description: Judith of HABSBURG was born on March 13, 1271 in Habsburg, Aargau, Switzerland, daughter of Rudolph I of HABSBURG and Gertrud Anna of HOHENBURG., they had 4 children. She died on May 21, 1297 in Prague, Prague Capital City, Czech Republic. This information is part of Pop Oswald Tree by Peter John Oswald on Genealogy Online.
